---
import { CldImage } from 'astro-cloudinary';
import Prose from '../Prose.astro';
import JlptCanDoChart from '../features/JlptCanDoChart.astro';
---

<!-- Stop Learning, Start Absorbing Section -->
<section class='py-16 lg:py-24 space-y-24'>
  <!-- Design: Google x Duolingo Redesign -->
  <div class='flex flex-col gap-10 lg:gap-16'>
    <!-- 1. Hero Headline & Problem/Solution Split -->
    <div class='space-y-12'>
      <div class='text-center space-y-4 max-w-4xl mx-auto'>
        <h2
          class='text-3xl lg:text-5xl font-black tracking-tight leading-tight'
        >
          Berhenti "Belajar Keras". <br />
          <span
            class='text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-linear-to-r from-(--token-purple-base) to-(--token-secondary-gold-base)'
          >
            Mulailah "Menyerap" Aja.
          </span>
        </h2>
        <p class='text-base md:text-xl text-(--token-text-secondary)'>
          Metode tradisional minta kamu jadi robot. Kami minta kamu jadi
          manusia.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div
        class='grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6'
        role='group'
        aria-label='Perbandingan: Metode Belajar Keras (tradisional) vs Menyerap Alami (immersion)'
      >
        <!-- Card A: Old Way -->
        <div
          class='p-6 md:p-8 rounded-3xl bg-[oklch(0.167_0_0)] border border-white/5 relative overflow-hidden group'
        >
          <div
            class='absolute inset-0 bg-linear-to-br from-red-500/5 to-transparent opacity-50'
          >
          </div>
          <div class='relative z-10'>
            <div class='flex items-center gap-3 mb-6 text-red-400'>
              <svg
                xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'
                width='24'
                height='24'
                viewBox='0 0 24 24'
                fill='none'
                stroke='currentColor'
                stroke-width='2'
                stroke-linecap='round'
                stroke-linejoin='round'
                class='lucide lucide-triangle-alert'
                ><path
                  d='m21.73 18-8-14a2 2 0 0 0-3.48 0l-8 14A2 2 0 0 0 4 21h16a2 2 0 0 0 1.73-3Z'
                ></path><path d='M12 9v4'></path><path d='M12 17h.01'
                ></path></svg
              >
              <span class='font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-sm'
                >Old Way</span
              >
            </div>
            <h3 class='text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white'>
              Belajar Keras
            </h3>
            <ul class='space-y-3 text-gray-400'>
              <li class='flex gap-2 items-start'>
                <span class='text-red-500 shrink-0 mt-1'>âœ•</span>
                <span>Hafal Rumus Bunpou & Latihan Soal</span>
              </li>
              <li class='flex gap-2 items-start'>
                <span class='text-red-500 shrink-0 mt-1'>âœ•</span>
                <span>Terjemahin Kalimat di Kepala</span>
              </li>
              <li class='flex gap-2 items-start'>
                <span class='text-red-500 shrink-0 mt-1'>âœ•</span>
                <span>Merasa Bersalah pas Capek</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Card B: New Way -->
        <div
          class='p-6 md:p-8 rounded-3xl bg-linear-to-br from-(--token-purple-base)/10 to-(--token-secondary-gold-base)/10 border border-(--token-purple-base)/20 relative overflow-hidden group'
        >
          <div class='absolute inset-0 bg-(--token-purple-base)/5 blur-3xl'>
          </div>
          <div class='relative z-10'>
            <div
              class='flex items-center gap-3 mb-6 text-(--token-secondary-gold-base)'
            >
              <svg
                xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'
                width='24'
                height='24'
                viewBox='0 0 24 24'
                fill='none'
                stroke='currentColor'
                stroke-width='2'
                stroke-linecap='round'
                stroke-linejoin='round'
                class='lucide lucide-sparkles'
                ><path
                  d='M9.937 15.5A2 2 0 0 0 8.5 14.063l-6.135-1.582a.5.5 0 0 1 0-.962L8.5 9.936A2 2 0 0 0 9.937 8.5l1.582-6.135a.5.5 0 0 1 .963 0L14.063 8.5A2 2 0 0 0 15.5 9.937l6.135 1.581a.5.5 0 0 1 0 .964L15.5 14.063a2 2 0 0 0-1.437 1.437l-1.582 6.135a.5.5 0 0 1-.963 0z'
                ></path><path d='M20 3v4'></path><path d='M22 5h-4'></path><path
                  d='M4 17v2'></path><path d='M5 18H3'></path></svg
              >
              <span class='font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-sm'
                >Immersion Way</span
              >
            </div>
            <h3 class='text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white'>
              Menyerap Alami; Immersion
            </h3>
            <ul class='space-y-3 text-(--token-text-secondary)'>
              <li class='flex gap-2 items-start'>
                <span class='text-(--token-secondary-green-base) shrink-0 mt-1'
                  >âœ“</span
                >
                <span>Nikmati Konten (Anime/Drama/Manga)</span>
              </li>
              <li class='flex gap-2 items-start'>
                <span class='text-(--token-secondary-green-base) shrink-0 mt-1'
                  >âœ“</span
                >
                <span>Intuisi Kebentuk Sendiri</span>
              </li>
              <li class='flex gap-2 items-start'>
                <span class='text-(--token-secondary-green-base) shrink-0 mt-1'
                  >âœ“</span
                >
                <span>Lagi Capek? Rebahan Aja Boleh</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 2. Hero Core Message -->
    <div class='text-center py-4'>
      <h3
        class='text-2xl md:text-4xl font-bold leading-relaxed max-w-4xl mx-auto'
      >
        <span class='text-(--token-text-muted)'>Intinya sederhana:</span><br
          class='mb-2'
        />
        Berhenti <span
          class='bg-red-500/10 text-red-300 px-3 py-1 rounded-lg decoration-red-500/50 line-through decoration-2 mx-1'
          >"belajar"</span
        >, mulailah <span
          class='bg-(--token-purple-base)/20 text-(--token-purple-base) px-3 py-1 rounded-lg mx-1'
          >"menyerap"</span
        >.
      </h3>
    </div>

    <!-- 3. Scenario Grid Cards -->
    <div>
      <h3
        class='text-center text-xl font-bold mb-10 text-(--token-text-secondary)'
      >
        Metode ini works bahkan di hari terburukmu:
      </h3>
      <div class='grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6'>
        <!-- Card 1: Capek -->
        <div
          class='group p-6 rounded-2xl bg-(--token-bg-light)/5 border border-white/5 hover:bg-(--token-bg-light)/10 transition-all hover:-translate-y-1'
        >
          <div class='flex items-center gap-4 mb-4'>
            <div
              class='w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-blue-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-blue-400 shrink-0 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform'
            >
              <!-- Bed Icon -->
              <svg
                xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'
                width='24'
                height='24'
                viewBox='0 0 24 24'
                fill='none'
                stroke='currentColor'
                stroke-width='2'
                stroke-linecap='round'
                stroke-linejoin='round'
                class='lucide lucide-bed'
                ><path d='M2 4v16'></path><path d='M2 8h18a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v10'
                ></path><path d='M2 17h20'></path><path d='M6 8v9'></path></svg
              >
            </div>
            <h4 class='text-lg font-bold'>Lagi Capek? ğŸ˜«</h4>
          </div>
          <p class='text-sm text-gray-400 leading-relaxed'>
            Otak udah ngebul? Cukup putar audio podcast Jepang sambil rebahan 15
            menit. Nggak usah mikir.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 2: Sibuk -->
        <div
          class='group p-6 rounded-2xl bg-(--token-bg-light)/5 border border-white/5 hover:bg-(--token-bg-light)/10 transition-all hover:-translate-y-1'
        >
          <div class='flex items-center gap-4 mb-4'>
            <div
              class='w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-orange-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-orange-400 shrink-0 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform'
            >
              <!-- Headphones Icon -->
              <svg
                xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'
                width='24'
                height='24'
                viewBox='0 0 24 24'
                fill='none'
                stroke='currentColor'
                stroke-width='2'
                stroke-linecap='round'
                stroke-linejoin='round'
                class='lucide lucide-headphones'
                ><path d='M3 14v3a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h2a2 2 0 0 0 2-2v-3'></path><path
                  d='M3 14h6'></path><path
                  d='M21 14v3a2 2 0 0 1-2 2h-2a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-3'></path><path
                  d='M15 14h6'></path><path
                  d='M21 12c0-3.3-2.7-6-6-6h-6c-3.3 0-6 2.7-6 6'></path></svg
              >
            </div>
            <h4 class='text-lg font-bold'>Lagi Sibuk? ğŸƒ</h4>
          </div>
          <p class='text-sm text-gray-400 leading-relaxed'>
            Dengar pas di jalan, di kereta, atau pas lagi masak. Manfaatkan
            "waktu mati" mu tanpa mengganggu jadwal.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 3: Males -->
        <div
          class='group p-6 rounded-2xl bg-(--token-bg-light)/5 border border-white/5 hover:bg-(--token-bg-light)/10 transition-all hover:-translate-y-1'
        >
          <div class='flex items-center gap-4 mb-4'>
            <div
              class='w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-purple-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-purple-400 shrink-0 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform'
            >
              <!-- TV Icon -->
              <svg
                xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'
                width='24'
                height='24'
                viewBox='0 0 24 24'
                fill='none'
                stroke='currentColor'
                stroke-width='2'
                stroke-linecap='round'
                stroke-linejoin='round'
                class='lucide lucide-tv'
                ><rect width='20' height='15' x='2' y='7' rx='2' ry='2'
                ></rect><polyline points='17 2 12 7 7 2'></polyline></svg
              >
            </div>
            <h4 class='text-lg font-bold'>Lagi Males? ğŸ¦¥</h4>
          </div>
          <p class='text-sm text-gray-400 leading-relaxed'>
            Tonton anime dengan subtitle Jepang aja. Nikmati ceritanya, nggak
            usah dipaksa paham 100%. No pressure.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 4. Coach's Note -->
    <div
      class='p-6 md:p-8 rounded-2xl bg-(--token-bg-light)/5 border-l-4 border-(--token-secondary-gold-base) backdrop-blur-sm'
    >
      <div class='flex gap-3 md:gap-5 items-start'>
        <div class='shrink-0 text-(--token-secondary-gold-base) mt-1'>
          <svg
            xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'
            width='32'
            height='32'
            viewBox='0 0 24 24'
            fill='none'
            stroke='currentColor'
            stroke-width='2'
            stroke-linecap='round'
            stroke-linejoin='round'
            class='lucide lucide-info'
            ><circle cx='12' cy='12' r='10'></circle><path d='M12 16v-4'
            ></path><path d='M12 8h.01'></path></svg
          >
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4 class='font-bold text-lg text-white mb-2'>Satu Hal Penting...</h4>
          <p class='text-(--token-text-secondary) leading-relaxed'>
            Kami nggak janji instan. Immersion tetap butuh waktu investasiâ€”kamu
            harus rutin "menyerap" bahasa itu berbulan-bulan. Tapi bedanya,
            prosesnya <span class='text-white font-medium'
              >ringan, menyenangkan, dan nggak bikin burnout</span
            >. Karena otakmu memang diciptakan untuk belajar bahasa dengan cara
            ini sejak lahir.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Feature 1: No Grammar -->
  <!-- Feature 1: No Grammar -->
  <div
    class='flex flex-col gap-6 lg:grid lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-20 items-center'
  >
    <!-- Image (Mobile Order 2, Desktop Left) -->
    <div
      class='order-2 lg:order-0 lg:col-start-1 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-white/10 shadow-2xl skew-y-1 lg:skew-y-2 hover:skew-y-0 transition-transform duration-500 w-full'
    >
      <CldImage
        src='Nggak_Bikin_Kamu_Lancar_Image_76q5so76q5so76q5_k7mexu'
        alt='Ilustrasi: Hafal grammar tidak bikin lancar'
        width={1696}
        height={2528}
        quality='auto'
        format='auto'
        loading='lazy'
        class='block w-full h-auto rounded-2xl'
      />
    </div>

    <!-- Text Wrapper (Mobile: Hidden/Contents, Desktop: Flex Column) -->
    <div class='contents lg:flex lg:flex-col gap-6 lg:justify-center w-full'>
      <!-- Header (Mobile Order 1, Desktop Top) -->
      <div class='order-1 flex items-start gap-4'>
        <div
          class='shrink-0 p-3 rounded-xl bg-red-500/10 border border-red-500/20 text-red-400 mt-1'
        >
          <svg
            xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'
            width='24'
            height='24'
            viewBox='0 0 24 24'
            fill='none'
            stroke='currentColor'
            stroke-width='2'
            stroke-linecap='round'
            stroke-linejoin='round'
            class='lucide lucide-x-circle'
            ><circle cx='12' cy='12' r='10'></circle><path d='m15 9-6 6'
            ></path><path d='m9 9 6 6'></path></svg
          >
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3
            class='text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2 leading-tight'
          >
            Kenapa Hafal Bunpou (Grammar) Nggak Bikin Kamu Lancar?
          </h3>
          <div
            class='h-1 w-20 bg-linear-to-r from-red-500 to-transparent rounded-full'
          >
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Text Body (Mobile Order 3, Desktop Bottom) -->
      <div class='order-3'>
        <Prose class='prose-lg prose-invert'>
          <p>
            Hafal bunpou itu kayak hafal rumus fisika: kamu tahu teorinya, bisa
            ngerjain soal di kertas, tapi pas dipraktikkin di dunia nyata,
            otakmu loading lama. Kenapa? Karena bahasa hidup nggak berjalan
            kayak rumus matematika. Native speaker Jepang nggak mikir "ini pakai
            partikel wa atau ga ya?" sebelum ngomongâ€”they just know, karena
            intuisi mereka sudah terbentuk dari kecil lewat mendengar dan
            melihat bahasa itu setiap hari.
          </p>
          <p>
            Kalau kamu mulai dari hafal bunpou, intuisi itu malah nggak
            terbentuk. Yang ada otakmu terbiasa "menganalisa" dulu baru ngomong,
            jadi gagap, lambat, dan aksennya kental Indonesia.
          </p>

          <JlptCanDoChart />

          <p>
            Data dari situs Resmi JLPT "Can-do" sendiri nunjukin: banyak yang
            lulus N4-N1 tapi masih susah paham percakapan kasual atau formal.
            Bukan karena mereka bodoh, tapi karena pondasinya salah dari awal.
          </p>
        </Prose>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Feature 2: No Translation -->
  <!-- Feature 2: No Translation -->
  <div
    class='flex flex-col gap-6 lg:grid lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-20 items-center'
  >
    <!-- Image (Mobile Order 2, Desktop Left) -->
    <div
      class='order-2 lg:order-0 lg:col-start-1 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-white/10 shadow-2xl -skew-y-1 lg:-skew-y-2 hover:skew-y-0 transition-transform duration-500 w-full'
    >
      <CldImage
        src='Itu_Bikin_Makin_Gagap_Image_76q5so76q5so76q5_jpipnb'
        alt='Ilustrasi: Menerjemahkan di kepala bikin gagap'
        width={1696}
        height={2528}
        quality='auto'
        format='auto'
        loading='lazy'
        class='block w-full h-auto rounded-2xl'
      />
    </div>

    <!-- Text Wrapper (Mobile: Hidden/Contents, Desktop: Flex Column) -->
    <div class='contents lg:flex lg:flex-col gap-6 lg:justify-center w-full'>
      <!-- Header (Mobile Order 1, Desktop Top) -->
      <div class='order-1 flex items-start gap-4'>
        <div
          class='shrink-0 p-3 rounded-xl bg-red-500/10 border border-red-500/20 text-red-400 mt-1'
        >
          <svg
            xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'
            width='24'
            height='24'
            viewBox='0 0 24 24'
            fill='none'
            stroke='currentColor'
            stroke-width='2'
            stroke-linecap='round'
            stroke-linejoin='round'
            class='lucide lucide-brain-circuit'
            ><path
              d='M12 4.5a2.5 2.5 0 0 0-4.96-.46 2.5 2.5 0 0 0-1.98 3 2.5 2.5 0 0 0-1.32 4.24 3 3 0 0 0 .34 5.58 2.5 2.5 0 0 0 2.96 3.08 2.5 2.5 0 0 0 4.91.05L12 20V4.5Z'
            ></path><path d='M16 8V5c0-1.1.9-2 2-2'></path><path d='M12 13h4'
            ></path><path d='M12 18h6a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v1'></path><path d='M12 8h8'
            ></path></svg
          >
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3
            class='text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2 leading-tight'
          >
            Kenapa Terjemahin Langsung di Kepala Itu Bikin Makin Gagap?
          </h3>
          <div
            class='h-1 w-20 bg-linear-to-r from-red-500 to-transparent rounded-full'
          >
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Text Body (Mobile Order 3, Desktop Bottom) -->
      <div class='order-3'>
        <Prose class='prose-lg prose-invert'>
          <p>
            Setiap kali kamu terjemahin kalimat Jepang ke Indonesia di kepala
            (atau sebaliknya), kamu lagi latihan "bahasa ketiga": campuran
            Indonesia-Jepang yang aneh. Otakmu jadi terbiasa mikir dalam Bahasa
            Indonesia dulu, baru convert ke Jepangâ€”prosesnya lambat dan makan
            energi banget. Hasilnya? Pas ngomong sama native, kamu loading lama,
            kalimatnya kaku, dan sering salah struktur.
          </p>
          <p>
            Native nggak gitu. Mereka mikir langsung dalam bahasa mereka.
            Immersion bikin kamu juga gitu: lama-lama kamu "merasa" mana yang
            benar tanpa perlu terjemahin. Kamu mulai bisa bilang "Ita'!" secara
            spontan pas kaki kesandung, bukan mikir dulu "sakit itu bahasa
            Jepangnya apa ya?". Itu yang bikin bahasa terasa hidup, bukan mati
            kayak di buku pelajaran.
          </p>
        </Prose>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
